{
  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><p id=\"u5ef2e834\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">您可以给在文档中添加链接，以便读者可以随时访问同一文档其他部分的信息，或同一知识库的另一篇文档。</span></p><p id=\"u0bfde8c8\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u9e1ce36e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">链接目标可以是</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">段落标题、表格卡片或者脑图卡片</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。通过设置锚点，您可以为读者提供信息，而无需在不同页面上重复相同信息。</span></p><p id=\"uc5751ae3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ud0c6fda1\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">若要添加从文档某一部分跳转到同一文档其他部分的链接，请复制目标的链接，将目标链接粘贴到需要跳转的起点。</span></p><p id=\"uc86749b5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"xv8FW\"><span class=\"ne-text\">目标链接</span></h2><h4 id=\"ymTIW\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1、文档目标链接</span></h4><p id=\"u51b43734\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">每篇文档的链接中，最后一个 / 后的一串字符就是文档目标链接。若需要设置跳转到某一篇文档，就可以复制这一小段字符作为目标链接。</span></p><p id=\"ube3ecc59\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u177e3ed1\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573097664368-28c8bccb-f963-4817-8625-62932eda0f4c.png\" width=\"487\" id=\"ydjAp\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u66e89da2\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h4 id=\"HOFL0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2、文档内段落链接和卡片链接</span></h4><p id=\"u7a40bbb6\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"ud08dcdf3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在语雀文档，每个标题都有一个自动生成的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">段落链接</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，而每个脑图卡片和表格卡片也有一个自动生成的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">卡片链接，</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">这些链接都可以作为文档内或文档间跳转的目标链接。点击段落前的图标，或点击卡片的🔗图标即可复制目标链接。</span></p><p id=\"udfeee8e7\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u67bdfd7e\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573034537464-f0ff67f1-115d-488e-883b-1ed41fb0646a.png\" width=\"216\" id=\"YhSEm\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ufd431ff3\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573097383222-ccf11d60-e39d-4926-b654-ca3c8ed6519e.png\" width=\"439\" id=\"IlSOT\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"u7d7ac5cb\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573097412836-380324ad-60dc-41c9-ad4e-57d2e003c4e2.png\" width=\"489\" id=\"XJYgI\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ufaa5f697\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"rGuWK\"><span class=\"ne-text\">添加链接</span></h2><p id=\"u67edd2e1\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u0ee66139\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">复制好</span><a href=\"#xv8FW\" data-href=\"#xv8FW\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">目标链接</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">，就可以为起点添加链接了。</span></p><p id=\"ubfeec8cb\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u713a6ddf\"><span class=\"ne-text\">选择要用作超链接的文本。</span></li><li id=\"ua36fe3cc\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击工具栏上方插入链接</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573098683764-ab519f35-735b-42a5-a904-85abeeb1cd69.png\" width=\"21\" id=\"Sav4s\" class=\"ne-image\"></li><li id=\"u50335b34\"><span class=\"ne-text\">将刚才复制的目标链接粘贴到弹窗中，并点击确定</span></li></ol><p id=\"uf482c1cf\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573098951279-c7cf34d2-8233-423e-87e7-8becd8e18265.png\" width=\"380\" id=\"PQPT8\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><ol start=\"4\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u792835ca\"><span class=\"ne-text\">跳转链接就设置成功啦</span></li></ol><p id=\"uecae467d\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/png/215718/1573098903536-729cbd20-ea18-4a18-9b30-33d43ec8eab4.png\" width=\"295\" id=\"hQgtC\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"uca16a809\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u67031c71\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"u28cff687\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道</span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">， 感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
  "slug": 13900821,
  "title": "如何设置文档内跳转和文档间跳转"
}